Rmd d097ffa akhooker 2025-02-26 Update enrichment plots

This script examines the degree of overlap between the SNPs covered by the MVP GWASes and the SNPs in Liyang’s ASoC annotation. We noticed high standard errors and negative enrichment values in our enrichment analysis, which may be due to SNPs in the ASoC annotation that are missing from the MVP GWAS.
